<ol>
  <li>create new service called 'api'</li>
  <li>add 1 method to service to get the contacts from the api located at 'http://localhost:4201/heroes'</li>
  <li>create new component named 'list'</li>
  <li>in the component, add the api service and get the list of contacts.</li>
  <li>display the list on the frontend.</li>
  <li>There should be a heading (h2) with the title 'Tour of Heroes'.</li>
</ol>
